{"title": "Tales Grotesque and Curious", "description": "Here collected are eleven of the over 200 stories that Ry\u016bnosuke Akutagawa wrote during his all-too-brief lifetime and give a sample of the odd and quirky world in which he dwells. Herein can be found eccentric parables such as the tricky demon of \"Tobacco and the Devil\", the skin-crawling \"Lice\" and the weird \"The Wine Worm\". But Akutagawa was also a master of the subtle character study illustrated by such tales as \"The Handkerchief\" and \"Mori Sensei\". Also included is \"Rashomon\", the dark and rain-swept inspiration for the acclaimed Akira Kurosawa film of the same name. (Summary by Ben Tucker)", "duration": 11125, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "3091", "name": "Ry\u016bnosuke Akutagawa"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/talesgrotesqueandcurious_2603_librivox/talesgrotesqueandcurious_2602.jpg", "copyright_year": "1930", "genres": ["Fantastic Fiction", "Single Author Collections"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Ben Tucker"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Ben Tucker"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Christine Rottger"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Christine Rottger"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Introduction", "readers": [16758], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/talesgrotesqueandcurious_2603_librivox/talesgrotesquecurious_00_akutagawa_64kb.mp3", "duration": 723}, {"section": 1, "title": "Tobacco and the Devil", "readers": [16758], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/talesgrotesqueandcurious_2603_librivox/talesgrotesquecurious_01_akutagawa_64kb.mp3", "duration": 978}, {"section": 2, "title": "The Nose", "readers": [16758], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/talesgrotesqueandcurious_2603_librivox/talesgrotesquecurious_02_akutagawa_64kb.mp3", "duration": 985}, {"section": 3, "title": "The Handkerchief", "readers": [16758], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/talesgrotesqueandcurious_2603_librivox/tale